body_html:
Thanks @jcomfort4. After Cloud SDK update 171.0.0 I had the same issue. Solved with
tensorboard --logdir=output
as replacement for:
python -m tensorflow.tensorboard --logdir=output
Please update: https://cloud.google.com/ml-engine/docs/how-tos/getting-started-training-prediction
